Summary values for TDL interpolated tanks and reference

extract_cycle_timing()

Cycle timing

Replace NA and NAN values in TDL$data by previous value for that variable

plot all variables with bs values, mean value, and CI intervals

f_plot_CI_individuals_driver()

plot each individual variable

create CI endpoints

update values for each bs iterate

Helper for f_val_bs_matrix, if the vector has zero length, return NA (for when using only TDL and not Licor)

This function calls all of the f_val_calc.* files

f_val_calc_corrected()

corrected (Corrected 12C, Corrected 13C)

f_val_calc_Cs()

Cs, ppm CO2 concentration at the leaf surface, cs calculated from eq 40 Ball 1987 Ch 20 Stomatal Function, eds Zeiger, Farquhar, Cowan

f_val_calc_delta_13C_Assim()

delta13C Assimilated, isotopic composition of assimilated sugars

f_val_calc_delta_13C_Resp()

delta13C Respired, isotopic composition of respired CO2

f_val_calc_Delta_from_A_ratio()

D from A ratio, (Ro/(13A/12A))-1, should be the same as Dobs above

f_val_calc_Delta_from_ratios_in_out()

Delta from ratios in and out?, (Re/Ro)-1, is this really the same?

f_val_calc_Delta_i_complex_for_gm()

Delta_i complex for gm CHECK DERIVATION predicted discrimination including boundary layer effects AND decarboxylation effects

f_val_calc_Delta_i_simple_for_gm()

Delta_i simple for gm, predicted discrimination including boundary layer effects but not decarboxylation effects

f_val_calc_Delta_i_simple_for_modeling()

Delta_i simple for modeling a + (b-a) pi/pa predicted discrimination including boundary layer effects but using b adjustments to approximate effects of gm and decarboxylations

f_val_calc_Delta_obs()

Delta, observed discrimination

f_val_calc_Delta_obs_permil()

Delta per mil, observed discrimination

f_val_calc_delta_permil()

delta permil (Isotopic composition (d) per mil)

f_val_calc_delta_proportion()

delta as proportion (Isotopic composition (d) as fraction)

f_val_calc_flow_adjusted()

Adjusted flow

f_val_calc_gain()

gain (12C Gain, 13C Gain)

f_val_calc_gm_point_complex()

gm point complex, internal leaf (mesophyll) conductance calculated for every D value estimating decarboxylation effects

f_val_calc_gm_point_simple()

gm point simple, internal leaf (mesophyll) conductance calculated for every D value ignoring decarboxylation effects

f_val_calc_gtc()

gtc, total (stomatal and boundary layer) conductance for CO2

f_val_calc_isotope_ratio()

Isotope ratio

f_val_calc_offset()

offset (12C Offset, 13C Offset) using hi tank

f_val_calc_p()

p

f_val_calc_pc_using_complex_Delta_full_model()

pc using complex D, full model [ab(pa-ps)+a(ps-pi)+pi(bs+al)-(eRd/k+fG*)-Dpa]/(bs+al-b) includes boundary layer and decarboxylation effects

f_val_calc_pc_using_complex_Delta_no_decarboxylation()

pc using complex D, no decarboxylation [ab(pa-ps)+a(ps-pi)+pi(bs+al)-Dpa]/(bs+al-b) is this different from two up? They give different values but both may not be derived properly

f_val_calc_pc_using_gm()

pc using gm, total partial pressure of CO2 at the site of carboxylation, Press is the atmospheric pressure value from the LI6400

f_val_calc_pc_using_simple_Delta_for_gm()

pc using simple D for gm, includes boundary layer

f_val_calc_pc_using_simple_Delta_for_modeling()

pc using simple D for modeling

f_val_calc_pp()

pa, partial pressure of CO2 above the leaf, Press is the atmospheric pressure value from the LI6400

f_val_calc_TDL_A_photosynthesis()

A, TDL photosynthesis

f_val_calc_total_mol_fraction_CO2()

Total mol fraction CO2

f_val_calc_xi()

xi
